ences==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Paul van Dyk}}\n{{Saint Etienne}}\n\n[[Category:2000 singles]]\n[[Category:Paul van Dyk songs]]\n[[Category:Saint Etienne (band) songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Bob Stanley (musician)]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Pete Wiggs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Paul van Dyk]]\n[[Category:UK Dance Singles Chart number-one singles]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Sarah Cracknell]]\n[[Category:2000 songs]]\n[[Category:Mute Records singles]]\n", "name_user": "68.194.62.51", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tell_Me_Why_(The_Riddle)"}
